= How to install a browser from the default browser choice =

== Boot into <code>Persistent Mode | SYSMAINT Session</code> ==

[[File:Boot-into-Sysmaint-session-1.svg|600px]]

== Press on <code>Install a Browser</code> ==

[[File:Choose-Install-a-Browser-2.svg|1000px]]

== Select one of the browsers from the list ==

[[File:Default-list-of-browsers-3.png|600px]]

== Select Firefox (as an example) ==

Press on <code>Continue</code> after you choose your favorite browser.

[[File:Choose-Firefox-4.png|600px]]

== Source of installation ==

[[File:Install-Firefox-From-Debian-5.png|600px]]

Choices for installation:

* Either from Debian repository which is going to be the [https://www.firefox.com/en-US/browsers/enterprise/ ESR version].
* [https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/all/desktop-release/ Rapid Release] version from firefox official repository.
* The [https://flathub.org/en/apps/org.mozilla.firefox Rapid Release] version of Firefox, verified and uploaded to the Flathub repository.

Tick: <code>Install</code>

<code>Dont update software database before installation</code>: Means do not run <code>apt update</code> before installing the package.

== Which command is going to run ==

[[File:How-the-command-to-install-it-6.png|600px]]

== Wait for the installation to complete ==

[[File:Wait-until-the-operation-finish-7.png|600px]]

Then press on <code>Continue</code> once finished.

== Installation finished ==

Press on <code>Done</code> then restart/reboot the system.

[[File:Installation-completed-8.png|600px]]

== Boot into <code>USER Session</code> ==

[[File:boot-into-user-session-9.svg|600px]]

== Run Firefox ==

[[File:Find-Firefox-10.png|600px]]

== Done ==

[[File:Run-Firefox-11.png|800px]]

